Title: Cargo
Writer: Arnold Bucher (story), Ivan Engler (story), Arnold Bucher (screenplay), Ivan Engler (screenplay), Patrik Steinmann (screenplay), Thilo Röscheisen (screenplay), Johnny Hartmann (screenplay)
Actors: Anna Katharina Schwabroh, Martin Rapold, Regula Grauwiller, Yangzom Brauen
Plot: Dr. Laura P. takes a job on a cargo spaceship for 4 years plus 4 years back. She'll join her sister on Rhea. 44 months later, in Laura's shift, strange things happen in cargo. The crew is reanimated and the captain dies mysteriously.
